dc_description_s: Summary appraisal data aggregated by neighborhood. Includes all taxable and exempt property for the entire City. City of Minneapolis Assessor's Office Column Definitions NN - Neighborhood number Neighborhood - Neighborhood name PINCount - Count of the number of property identification numbers, which are unique to each parcel and condo unit HMCount - Total number of properties with homestead status RelHMCount - Total number of properties with relative homestead status MidHMCount - Total number of properties with mid-year homestead status UnitCount - Total number of rentable living units RoomCount - Total number of rentable rooms NewConsCount - Total number of properties with a new construction amount ResEMV - Total residential estimated market value AptEMV - Total apartment estimated market value CI_EMV - Total commercial and industrial estimated market value TCSum - Total tax capacity (tax capacity equals estimated market value times statutory class rate by parcel) ExemptEMV - Total estimated market value for exempt properties
